with the drunk-sounding "zero"

151
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:19,600
of a man saying "my girlfriend left me,
but guess how many fucks he gives ?

152
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,640
Zeeeeerrrrrrrrrrroooooooooo !

