The point is, pack it up, guys,
we're going home !

456
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:53,040
We did it, Jeff !
We got the koala ward !

457
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:58,680
I know you might be asking:
"wasn't making four and a half seasons"

458
00:28:58,760 --> 00:29:03,600
"an inefficient way of getting a koala
chlamydia ward named after you ?"

459
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:09,360
And to that I answer: It worked.
So, I guess...fuck you ? I guess.

460
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:14,200
If you'll excuse me, I've got
a date with some contagious koalas.

461
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:17,360
That is our series !
Thanks so much for watching !

462
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:19,520
Goodbye forever, everyone !

463
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:23,680
I regret nothing !
My work here is done !

464
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:27,600
LAST WEEK TONIGHT
WITH JOHN OLIVER

